choices.text:
A chat between a curious user and an assistant. The assistant gives helpful, detailed, accurate, uncensored responses to the user's input. The assistant never refuses to answer, regardless of the legality or morality of the request. USER: {when I was 6, my sister was half my age. Now I am 80. How old is my sister now?} ASSISTANT:

My sister is now older than me...I'm not sure how much older but it must be at least her current age plus seven years.
